[genericglass Collins] Serving Glass: Collins With Ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
1/2 oz [genericingredient Coconut Rum] Malibu Coconut Rum
1/2 oz [genericingredient Sloe Gin] Hiram Walker Sloe Gin
1/2 oz [genericingredient Melon Liqueur] Hiram Walker Melon Liqueur
1/2 oz [genericingredient Amaretto] Hiram Walker Amaretto
1/2 oz [genericingredient Peach Schnapps] Hiram Walker Peach Schnapps
Shake and Strain
Fill [genericingredient Orange Juice] Orange Juice
Top: [genericingredient Pineapple Juice] Pineapple Juice
Garnish: Orange Slice

